text: Rosenhain is surname of: * Johann Georg Rosenhain (1816 - 1887), German mathematician * Jakob (Jacob, Jacques) Rosenhain (1813, Mannheim – 1894, Baden-Baden), a Jewish German pianist and composer * Walter Rosenhain (1875, Berlin – 1934), an Australian metallurgist == See also == * Category:German- language surnames Category:Jewish surnames Category:Yiddish-language surnames
